        <figure class="figure-primary"><div class="image-container">
                <img src="http://bhfcpnp.medsci.ox.ac.uk/upcoming-events/training-course-pragmatic-evaluation-in-physical-activity-public-health/@@images/image/feature" class="img-responsive" /><cite>
